### 1. 创建智能体平台信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{routerPrefix}}/intelligent_access
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "accessName": "dify",
  "accessType": "DifyEnterprise",
  "dbHost": "0.tcp.jp.ngrok.io",
  "dbPort": 14224,
  "dbUser": "postgres",
  "dbPassword": "difyai123456",
  "dbName": "dify"
}

### 2. 更新智能体平台信息
